teams of the two countries will keep contact with each other to
probe the problem of Young Pioneers in Malawi who had supported
former Malawian President H. K. Banda before fleeing to
Mozambique.
</P>
<P>
The mixed committee meeting had been focusing on crime issues
such as weapon and drug smuggling, money laundrying and car
theft. 
