<TEXT>
<P>
LHASA, February 12 (Xinhua) -- Jangzhong Zhaxi Doje, former
vice-chairman of the Tibet Autonomous Regional Committee of the
Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC),
died of illness on February 9 at the age of 73.
</P>
<P>
Pagbalha Geleg Namgyai, vice-chairman of the Standing Committee
of the National People's Congress and a number of Tibetan local
leaders attended today's funeral.
</P>
