Doje served as the vice-mayor of Lhasa, vice-chairman of the
Third Tibet Autonomous Regional Committee of the CPPCC,
vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of the Fourth and Fifth
Tibet Autonomous Regioal committees of the National People's
Congress, and as a deputy to the Sixth and Seventh NPC and a
member of the Eighth National Committee of the CPPCC.
