have been able to return to production, allowing a large number of
employees to return to their jobs.
</P>
<P>
Some other enterprises are setting up various companies to
employ laid-off workers. The Yanzhou Mining Administration, a
major coal producer, has put half of its employees into other
businesses.
</P>
