previous four trading days, but the overall trend was solid.
</P>
<P>
With no fresh incentives to improve the Japanese economic
outlook, players are still waiting for additional economic
stimulus measures to be unveiled by the ruling Liberal Democratic
Party ahead of a meeting February 21 in London of top financial
officials of the Group of 7 industrialized nations, the traders
said.
</P>
<P>
Of the 1,327 issues listed on the First Section, gainers
outpaced losers 703 to 472, with 199 issues remaining unchanged.
