<HEADLINE> Norwegian Sondral Wins Men's 1,000m Speed Skating </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAGANO, Japan, February 12 (Xinhua) -- Norwegian Aadne Sondral took
a surprise gold medal for the men's 1,000-meter speed skating race
