<HEADLINE> Burkina Faso Edges Algeria 2-1 in African Nations' Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, February 11 (Xinhua) -- Burkina Faso defeated Algeria
2-1 in their African Nations' Cup group A match in Ouagadougou,
Burkina Faso on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Both sides scored no goal in the first half.
</P>
