<HEADLINE> Five Countries Bid for 2004 Euro Soccer Championship </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, February 11 (Xinhua) -- Five countries have submitted
their bids to stage the finals of the 2004 European soccer
championship, European soccer ruling body UEFA said in Nyon on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
