Cameroon goalkeeper Jacques Songo ventured out but Souleymane
Oulare shot the ball wide off an open goal.
</P>
<P>
Cameroon added a second goal three minutes from halftime
through Nlend Wome.
</P>
<P>
One minute into second half, Cameroon's goalkeeper twice
fumbled a cross from the left and Oulare had an easy job to roll
the ball home from close-range.
</P>
<P>
Oulare hit a second with 15 minutes left, sending the Guinean
fans wild. 
